725445f-a.title: Queens: 53rd Street - Roosevelt Avenue
725445f-a.text:
53rd Street, south of Roosevelt Ave., viewed from the Lincoln Ave.
elevated station of the B.M.T; I.R.T., subway lines. This is a south-
easterly view, showing in the background the New York Connecting Rail-
road Bridge.
0ctober 1, 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
